body_html:
@angersson Thanks for the reply! This seems to be a common problem for ops in tf.contrib. I was wondering if this could be solved by registering the TRTEngineOp (generated by TensorRT) to the Op dict and if someone can fix that for future release. Just want to make sure that people who work on TF-TRT are aware of this issue.

Problem solved after build 1.7.0 from source. Was on release candidate 1.
